/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/README.md:3:# 🧠 memory-lancedb-pro · 🦞OpenClaw Plugin\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/README.md:13:[![npm version](https://img.shields.io/npm/v/memory-lancedb-pro)](https://www.npmjs.com/package/memory-lancedb-pro)\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/README.md:17:<h2>⚡ <a href=\"https://github.com/CortexReach/memory-lancedb-pro/releases/tag/v1.1.0-beta.10\">v1.1.0-beta.10 — OpenClaw 2026.3+ Hook Adaptation</a></h2>\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/README.md:31:## Why memory-lancedb-pro?\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/README.md:35:**memory-lancedb-pro** is a production-grade long-term memory plugin for OpenClaw that turns your agent into an **AI Memory Assistant** — it automatically captures what matters, lets noise naturally fade, and retrieves the right memory at the right time. No manual tagging, no configuration headaches.\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/README.md:47:**With memory-lancedb-pro — your agent learns and remembers:**\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/README.md:76:The community-maintained **[setup script](https://github.com/CortexReach/toolbox/tree/main/memory-lancedb-pro-setup)** handles install, upgrade, and repair in one command:\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/README.md:79:curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/CortexReach/toolbox/main/memory-lancedb-pro-setup/setup-memory.sh -o setup-memory.sh\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/README.md:89:openclaw plugins install memory-lancedb-pro@beta\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/README.md:94:npm i memory-lancedb-pro@beta\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/README.md:103:    \"slots\": { \"memory\": \"memory-lancedb-pro\" },\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/README.md:105:      \"memory-lancedb-pro\": {\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/README.md:137:openclaw logs --follow --plain | grep \"memory-lancedb-pro\"\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/README.md:141:- `memory-lancedb-pro: smart extraction enabled`\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/README.md:142:- `memory-lancedb-pro@...: plugin registered`\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/README.md:152:2. Bind the memory slot: `plugins.slots.memory = \"memory-lancedb-pro\"`\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/README.md:153:3. Verify: `openclaw plugins info memory-lancedb-pro && openclaw memory-pro stats`\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/README.md:180:Help me connect this memory plugin with the most user-friendly configuration: https://github.com/CortexReach/memory-lancedb-pro\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/README.md:202:memory-lancedb-pro is the core plugin. The community has built tools around it to make setup and daily use even smoother:\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/README.md:206:> **[CortexReach/toolbox/memory-lancedb-pro-setup](https://github.com/CortexReach/toolbox/tree/main/memory-lancedb-pro-setup)**\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/README.md:227:Built-in provider presets: **Jina / DashScope / SiliconFlow / OpenAI / Ollama**, or bring your own OpenAI-compatible API. For full usage (including `--ref`, `--selfcheck-only`, and more), see the [setup script README](https://github.com/CortexReach/toolbox/tree/main/memory-lancedb-pro-setup).\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/README.md:231:> **[CortexReach/memory-lancedb-pro-skill](https://github.com/CortexReach/memory-lancedb-pro-skill)**\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/README.md:233:Install this skill and your AI agent (Claude Code or OpenClaw) gains deep knowledge of every feature in memory-lancedb-pro. Just say **\"help me enable the best config\"** and get:\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/README.md:242:git clone https://github.com/CortexReach/memory-lancedb-pro-skill.git ~/.claude/skills/memory-lancedb-pro\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/README.md:247:git clone https://github.com/CortexReach/memory-lancedb-pro-skill.git ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/memory-lancedb-pro-skill\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/README.md:386:| Feature | Built-in `memory-lancedb` | **memory-lancedb-pro** |\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/README.md:520:| `llm.oauthPath` | string | `~/.openclaw/.memory-lancedb-pro/oauth.json` | OAuth token file used when `llm.auth` is `oauth` |\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/README.md:533:    \"oauthPath\": \"${HOME}/.openclaw/.memory-lancedb-pro/oauth.json\",\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/README.md:542:- OAuth tokens default to `~/.openclaw/.memory-lancedb-pro/oauth.json`.\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/README.md:601:4. After the callback succeeds, the command saves the plugin OAuth file (default: `~/.openclaw/.memory-lancedb-pro/oauth.json`), snapshots the previous api-key `llm` config for logout, and replaces the plugin `llm` config with OAuth settings (`auth`, `oauthProvider`, `model`, `oauthPath`)\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/README.md:615:{ \"plugins\": { \"entries\": { \"memory-lancedb-pro\": { \"config\": { \"autoRecall\": false } } } } }\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/README.md:629:{ \"plugins\": { \"entries\": { \"memory-lancedb-pro\": { \"config\": { \"autoRecallTimeoutMs\": 8000 } } } } }\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/README.md:687:Confirm you are editing memory-lancedb-pro vs built-in memory-lancedb before changes.\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/README.md:722:On LanceDB 0.26+, some numeric columns may be returned as `BigInt`. Upgrade to **memory-lancedb-pro >= 1.0.14** — this plugin now coerces values using `Number(...)` before arithmetic.\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/README.md:755:openclaw plugins info memory-lancedb-pro\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/README.md:770:  memory-lancedb-pro-session-memory: command:new\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/README.md:782:4. Verify: `openclaw plugins info memory-lancedb-pro` should show `Legacy before_agent_start: no`\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/README.md:816:> Status: Beta — available via `npm i memory-lancedb-pro@beta`. Stable users on `latest` are not affected.\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/README.md:824:Feedback: [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/CortexReach/memory-lancedb-pro/issues) · Revert: `npm i memory-lancedb-pro@latest`\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/README.md:852:Full list: [Contributors](https://github.com/CortexReach/memory-lancedb-pro/graphs/contributors)\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/README.md:856:<a href=\"https://star-history.com/#CortexReach/memory-lancedb-pro&Date\">\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/README.md:858:    <source media=\"(p