{"type":"message","id":"86a1f931","parentId":"c52e0dd9","timestamp":"2026-04-05T14:16:31.041Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\"command\":\"git status --short; cp ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json.bak.$(date +%Y%m%d-%H%M%S); perl -0pi -e 's/\\\"autoRecall\\\"\\\\s*:\\\\s*true/\\\"autoRecall\\\": false/' ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json; grep -n 'autoRecall' ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json | sed -n '1,20p'; openclaw gateway restart\",\"workdir\":\"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace\",\"yieldMs\":1000,\"timeout\":120,\"elevated\":true,\"ask\":\"on-miss\",\"security\":\"full\"}","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_08e897a0cfd47a720169d26eb6fff0819a99178ad985be3820\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 需要你先批准这条命令，我才能改配置并重启 gateway：\n\n/approve `git status --short; cp ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json.bak.$(date +%Y%m%d-%H%M%S); perl -0pi -e 's/\"autoRecall\"\\s*:\\s*true/\"autoRecall\": false/' ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json; grep -n 'autoRecall' ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json | sed -n '1,20p'; openclaw gateway restart`\n\n批准后我就继续。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_08e897a0cfd47a720169d26eb9db4c819ab827144dae7134c2\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":40984,"output":299,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41283,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775398577973,"responseId":"resp_08e897a0cfd47a720169d26eb544b8819aa89ee0a3e07fb0fa"}}
