{"type":"message","id":"e655caa1","parentId":"f9752978","timestamp":"2026-04-05T14:19:18.265Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_vnTcaqvwZBNZLHVHBSc8HLUu|fc_0be4e4864e2828620169d26f5e3f3c819aa46181481a5b9a75","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"fatal: not a git repository (or any parent up to mount point /)\nStopping at filesystem boundary (GIT_DISCOVERY_ACROSS_FILESYSTEM not set).\n261:          \"autoRecall\": false,\n262:          \"autoRecallMinLength\": 6,\nGateway service disabled.\nStart with: openclaw gateway install\nStart with: openclaw gateway\nStart with: systemctl --user start openclaw-gateway.service\nStart with: systemd user services are unavailable; install/enable systemd or run the gateway under your supervisor.\nStart with: If you're in a container, run the gateway in the foreground instead of `openclaw gateway`.\n\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"plaid-slug","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"fatal: not a git repository (or any parent up to mount point /)\nStopping at filesystem boundary (GIT_DISCOVERY_ACROSS_FILESYSTEM not set).\n261:          \"autoRecall\": false,\n262:          \"autoRecallMinLength\": 6,\nGateway service disabled.\nStart with: openclaw gateway install\nStart with: openclaw gateway\nStart with: systemctl --user start openclaw-gateway.service\nStart with: systemd user services are unavailable; install/enable systemd or run the gateway under your supervisor.\nStart with: If you're in a container, run the gateway in the foreground instead of `openclaw gateway`.\n","name":"git status"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775398758260}}
{"type":"message","id":"7ba1b157","parentId":"e655caa1","timestamp":"2026-04-05T14:19:43.388Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 改好了，结果如下：\n\n## 已完成\n- `autoRecall` 已经从 `true` 改成了 `false`\n- 备份也已保存了一份 `openclaw.json.bak.时间戳`\n\n## 但重启结果有个关键信息\n**gateway 没有被 systemd 托管，所以 `openclaw gateway restart` 没真正重启成功。**\n\n它返回的是：\n\n- `Gateway service disabled.`\n- `Start with: openclaw gateway`\n\n这说明现在这台环境里的 gateway 不是 systemd service 模式。\n\n---\n\n## 现在最实际的下一步\n你要做 B 组验证，还差一步：\n\n### 让当前 gateway 进程重新加载配置\n最直接有两种方式：\n\n#### 方式 1：如果你现在就是前台跑的\n重新启动当前 OpenClaw / gateway 进程\n\n#### 方式 2：直接手动启动\n运行：\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway\n```\n\n如果你平时不是这样启动的，那就按你原本启动 OpenClaw 的方式重新拉起来。\n\n---\n\n## 你现在可以怎么测\n在确保 gateway 重新启动后：\n\n1. 去飞书发一句：`你好`\n2. 看回复速度有没有明显变快\n\n---\n\n## 目前我能明确确认的\n### 已确认\n- B 组配置已切换成功：`autoRecall: false`\n\n### 还未确认\n- 新配置是否已经被当前运行中的 gateway 进程加载\n\n---\n\n## 一句话\n**B 组参数已经改了，但还需要你把当前 OpenClaw/gateway 重新启动一下，测试才有效。**\n\n如果你愿意，我下一步可以继续帮你：\n- 判断你这台机器上的 OpenClaw 现在到底是怎么启动的\n- 告诉你最准确的重启方式\n\n你回我一句：\n\n**继续查怎么重启**","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0be4e4864e2828620169d26f6d1928819a9b82effee90dec53\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":679,"output":427,"cacheRead":41216,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42322,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775398758266,"responseId":"resp_0be4e4864e2828620169d26f6af2c8819a9ca76c1a0de348d4"}}
