{"type":"message","id":"112e3ff6","parentId":"7fabe8e5","timestamp":"2026-04-05T15:13:53.698Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 你好，我在。  \n刚才我已经查到一个关键点：你现在这套上下文里，**LCM 的 `freshTailCount` 还是 32**，这个值偏大，确实可能拖慢响应。  \n\n如果你愿意，我下一步就直接给你一版 **最小改动提速配置**。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07cad9416604fe270169d27c0e7fdc819a904a73b02c2d960a\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":57002,"output":84,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57086,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775401989261,"responseId":"resp_07cad9416604fe270169d27c0cbaf4819a83aae8686a1d6185"}}
