{"type":"message","id":"b4a3b9a2","parentId":"86e28f52","timestamp":"2026-04-05T15:18:57.180Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 改好了。\n\n## 已修改\n- `freshTailCount: 32 → 12`\n\n现在你的提速组合是：\n\n- `autoRecall: false`\n- `freshTailCount: 12`\n\n---\n\n## 下一步\n你需要让当前运行中的 OpenClaw 重新加载配置，然后去飞书测一句：\n\n**你好**\n\n然后告诉我结果是下面哪种：\n- **明显快了**\n- **稍微快了一点**\n- **没区别**\n- **还是很慢**\n\n如果你已经重启好了，就直接去测。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_00ba8523c21a776f0169d27d5c6838819b85ea84f5ae5e0d17\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":57850,"output":125,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57975,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775402322500,"responseId":"resp_00ba8523c21a776f0169d27d5ac1e0819b9c5b5d0034e7f0db"}}
